<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink358">
<l>kōṭuyar paṉmalai yiṟantaṉa rāyiṉu</l>
<l>nīṭa viṭumō maṟṟē nīṭuniṉaintu</l>
<l>tuṭaittoṟun tuṭaittoṟuṅ kalaṅki</l>
<l>yuṭaitteḻu veḷḷa mākiya kaṇṇē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though [he] has crossed many mountains with towering peaks, </l>
<l>will your eyes forever remain a flood, </l>
<l>overflowing and rising as you weep, </l>
<l>wiping [your tears] again and again, </l>
<l>lost in thoughts [of him] for so long? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
